It was the weekend and the guys had promised BaileyBrooke and ShaneBlair they were going to taking them out. They hated waiting and made sure the girls got the message. After awhile it got pretty annoying and she could sense my anger but if there was anything that Bailey could do was calm right down. So she said fuck the guys and had a different idea on how we should spend our glorious weekend
